text: Robert Philip Hemmings (born 28 February 1996) is an English cricketer who most recently played for Derbyshire County Cricket Club. Primarily a right-arm fast-medium bowler, he also bats right handed. ==External links== * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:English cricketers Category:People from Stoke-on-Trent Category:Derbyshire cricketers Category:Staffordshire cricketers
